des:
You can use Alexa to control your Hyundai socket, light, strip, switch.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Hyundai Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Hyundai Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Hyundai Home account in our "Hyundai Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Hyundai Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Hyundai Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Hyundai Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Hyundai Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Hyundai Home", and you'll be navigated to Hyundai Home login page;
(9). Input your Hyundai Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
